Raw Republic is a very small hidden gem in Aventura that offers acai bowls, smoothies, and cold-press juices. As soon as you walk in, the staff will make you feel like home and will guide you through the menu until they help you find exactly what you’re in the mood for. Raw Republic offers the best acai bowls in Zone 2, which you can alter however you want by adding or removing any of their many ingredients. The cold-press juices are also very delicious. Once you try it, we guarantee you will be coming back for more.
